Feature: Calculate strike

  Scenario Outline: I hit a strike
    Given I roll the bowling ball as my first roll on a <frame>
    When I <hit> ten pins
    Then the frame <score> is ten plus the score of my next two rolls

    Examples:
    |frame| hit | score |
    |  1  |  10 |  30   |
    |  2  |  10 |  60   |
    |  3  |  10 |  90   |
    |  4  |  10 |  120  |
    |  5  |  10 |  150  |
    |  6  |  10 |  180  |
    |  7  |  10 |  210  |
    |  8  |  10 |  240  |
    |  9  |  10 |  270  |
    |  10 |  10 |  300  |